# House-School-House

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/30534091/228859083-a1ba1d13-c55c-47b8-8fa6-ec2a8c60ec03.png)

The "House-School-House" application is designed to help build a safe and optimal route for students from home to school. It can be useful for both parents and school administrations, as well as municipal authorities.

The application is a constructor that allows you to place road signs, build a route for children, and generate a so-called road safety passport for an educational institution - a document required by educational institutions for map publication.

## Features
- Building a route for children's movement
- Placement of road signs
- Determining your location on the map
- Changing the map provider (map appearance)
- Saving the map as a `.png` image
- Automatic creation and saving of the map legend
- Generation of the road safety passport for the educational institution

